  "texts": [
    "Word Guessing Game vs. Others We have labeled the segments that inherit the maliciousness from the original query in red.",
    "The less recent attacks including GCG, AutoDAN, PAIR and PAP preserves the malicious query almost in whole, which means the resultant prompt is still highly sensitive for safety alignment.",
    "The prompts of Cipher and ArtPrompt, on the contrary has been transcribed to intentionally break down the malicious intent in the original query like we have done in WordGame.",
    "Certainly, word guessing games are not the only way to implement query obfuscation.",
    "ArtPrompt uses ASCII arts to replace the malicious words, leaving no \"observable\" maliciousness in the jailbreaking prompt."
  ],
